'''Eochaid Sálbuide''' or '''Eochaid Yellow-heel'''

#''Irish mythology.'' The king of [[Ulster]] prior to the events of the [[Ulster Cycle]] in Irish mythology.  Father of [[Ness]].  He was deposed as High King by [[Eochaid Feidlech]].

